'''Endocrine cloister''' were [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[biot]]s used on [[Koros-Strohna|worldships]]. They used [[tii]].

[[Nen Yim]] used the [[Vul Ag protocol]] to fix the endocrine cloister on the ''[[Baanu Kor]]'', the first time it had been used for that purpose.

